{"tid":920550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞女色狼驚現葵涌　18歲小鮮肉驚青報警","createTime":"2018-11-29T01:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T02:24:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83122592cfdde83323c857d3807478d8186c8b15","tid":920550,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"18歲仔店舖內遭非禮，警追緝南亞女色狼。昨日(28日)晚上10時許，一名18歲青年於葵涌梨木道一店舖遭非禮。警方接報到場，經初步調查，追緝一名年約25歲南亞裔女子，約1.7米高，中等身材，長頭髮，案發時身穿黑色上衣。案件暫列非禮，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"1c3850d586c0ffbbca838266abe36bbcdfae50df","tid":920550,"uid":61529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好撚慘但我笑咗"},{"pid":"6fe1d3825940ea0dd4a38287d6c95b94cb438b1a","tid":920550,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b619a21f3df2e5d9f0589dd706b758580dfa5dc","tid":920550,"uid":41292,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"到底咩肉可以放18年"},{"pid":"b9091dfdad764db173eb371f1ab25d9484851835","tid":920550,"uid":157765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"鮮你老母肉"},{"pid":"b304105e089822b215911e0418e007a8ad45ed35","tid":920550,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"有得食都唔食 正一青頭仔"},{"pid":"bdd0762c796883afa69cd213d5b7f5d808fd02db","tid":920550,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b619a21f3df2e5d9f0589dd706b758580dfa5dc","tid":920550,"uid":41292,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"到底咩肉可以放18年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"金華火腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9482157097f2e55